\subsection{Observable Variables}
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

Table~\ref{tab:variables} summarizes the observable variables employed throughout the empirical analyses, their analytical roles, and the propositions to which they contribute. Rather than measuring the latent theoretical constructs directly, these variables operationalize the observable comparisons implied by the deductive framework.
